Pidgin PBar
===========

This Pidgin plugin adds a toolbar to the buddy list to quickly update nickname,
personal message, icon, status and mood. It also allows updating the current
song and other parameters which are updated globally on all accounts that
support them.

It is distributed under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 3.

1. Installation

You will need a C compiler like gcc, make and the following depencies :

  - pidgin-dev
  - gtk+-2.0
  - pkg-config

On Debian or Ubuntu use the following command as root to install those required packages :

  # aptitude install pidgin-dev libgtk2.0-dev pkg-config make gcc libc6-dev

Then enter the following command :

  $ make
  $ sudo make install

This will install the plugin and locales which can be disabled with the DISABLE_NLS flag and
debugging informations could be disabled with the WITHOUT_DEBUG flags.
